  "2-39": (
    caption: [FADH2 is a carrier of hydrogens and high-energy electrons, like NADH and NADPH. (A) Structure of FADH2, with its hydrogen-carrying atoms highlighted in yellow. (B) The formation of FADH2 from FAD (flavin adenine dinucleotide).],
